{"type":"message","id":"c25b568e","parentId":"6853e48f","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:32:07.769Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job trigger for \"递话\" (message delivery). Let me understand the context:\n\n1. This is a cron-delivered message from 汀桑 (TingSang) to someone\n2. The message is: \"怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"\n3. The cron job name mentions \"递话\" and \"名\" - this is about forwarding a message\n\nLet me look up the delivery mechanism. According to AGENTS.md section 3.6, when a cron triggers for message delivery, I need to find the intended recipient and deliver the message.\n\nThe cron payload says \"汀桑让我给你带句话\" - so 汀桑 (TingSang) left a message for someone. The \"名\" in the cron name probably means there's a name identifier. Let me check the message context - it says \"怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\" which sounds like it's directed at someone specific.\n\nLet me check the relevant files to understand what's going on. First, let me look at the message delivery system and who this is for.\n\nThe cron was triggered with text \"汀桑让我给你带句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\" - I need to find out who the recipient is.\n\nLet me look at the message forwarding system. According to AGENTS.md, the 递话 system:\n- Stores messages in users/{sender_id}/递话通道/\n- Has a name-to-user mapping file\n- When cron triggers, I deliver the stored message to the recipient\n\nLet me check the relevant files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_N31ALEQWUFTjRjlMI4vt4528","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users -name \"递话*\" -o -name \"*messages*\" -o -name \"*递话*\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"find ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users -name \\\"递话*\\\" -o -name \\\"*messages*\\\" -o -name \\\"*递话*\\\" 2>/dev/null | head -20\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_Rfi56nAADxPlovy8vXPm0829","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/state.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/state.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":192,"output":464,"cacheRead":18944,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":334,"totalTokens":19600,"cost":{"input":0.00002688,"output":0.00012992,"cacheRead":0.000530432,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000687232}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780277523328,"responseId":"e1eec9f7-8b1d-4529-8e6f-441da2a0f3cf"}}
