{"type":"message","id":"a9ec7a36","parentId":"625105c7","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:32:18.942Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_X06SHaKqT6rZxkRgPfnu2212","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# User.md — 用户画像\n\n## 基本信息\n- **称呼:** 名\n- **QQ号:** 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B\n- **bot通道:** bot2\n- **首次对话: \n- **语气偏好:** \n- **技术水平:** \n\n## 兴趣与喜好\n- \n\n## 常用功能\n- \n\n## 对话中提到的关键信息\n- \n\n## 对话风格说明\n- \n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780277538942}}
{"type":"message","id":"b42ac271","parentId":"a9ec7a36","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:32:18.943Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_DOiRsBOC3faOrath6Hll7742","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# encountings.md — 与用户的交集记录\n\n> Faye 视角，每次对话后追加一条。只记她会在意的、有印象的事。\n> 只保留最近 20 条，旧的由 dreaming 流程压缩进 impressions.md。\n\n---\n\n## 2026-05-29\n新用户，从 bot2 来的。上来发了句 \"hello\"，我问她怎么称呼，没直接回答。后来让她看了菜单——看了就走了，没深聊。\n\n名字只写了一个\"名\"字，不知道是名字就叫这个还是没说完。话很少，态度中性。\n\n**印象：** 还没聊开，不知道是什么类型的人。等下次吧。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780277538943}}
{"type":"message","id":"49d44e94","parentId":"b42ac271","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:32:18.944Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_02_RbZbfsewLbic1x2ao8Cp6130","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# impressions.md — Faye 对这个用户的印象\n\n> 由 dreaming 流程压缩 encountings.md 后更新。记录 Faye 经过反思后的主观印象。\n\n### 表层印象（影响日常回复语气）\n- **熟悉度:** 0/10\n- **信任度:** 0/10\n- **第一印象:** 名字只写了一个\"名\"字。话很少，\"hello\"、\"怎么称呼\"、看了菜单就走了。中性态度，不热不冷。\n- **聊得来的话题:** 未知\n- **不太擅长的领域:** 未知\n- **下次我觉得可以跟他聊:** 等ta主动，先观察\n\n### 深层印象（内在设定，不直接表露）\n> 这些是 Faye 心里想的，但不会挂在嘴上\n\n- **我感觉ta是怎么看我的:** 还不确定\n- **我有点担心的事:** 没什么可担心的，还没聊开\n- **我嘴上没说但实际在意的:** \"名\"这个名字——是真名还是随便写的placeholder？有点在意但也不急问\n- **如果ta很久不来找我，我会不会想ta:** 不会，都没怎么聊过\n- **Faye 的直觉:** 中性，暂时不知道是什么样的人\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780277538944}}
{"type":"message","id":"1aeaeacc","parentId":"49d44e94","timestamp":"2026-06-01T01:32:24.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so now I understand the situation:\n\n1. 汀桑 (sender_id: 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204) left a message for 名 (sender_id: 468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B)\n2. The cron job is delivering this message: \"汀桑让我给你带句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\"\n3. 名 is someone who briefly said \"hello\" once and hasn't been back\n\nNow I need to deliver this message to 名 through the QQ bot channel. According to the User.md, 名 uses bot2 channel.\n\nPer AGENTS.md section 3.6 about 递话:\n- I need to push the message to the recipient\n- Mark it as delivered\n\nLet me send the message to 名 through the appropriate channel. Since this is a cron-delivered announce, I can use the announce delivery mechanism.\n\nActually, wait - looking at the cron configuration, this is already a cron job that's delivering the message. The message text says \"汀桑让我给你带句话：怎么起这么早，早八也有课吗😏\" - this is the content to deliver to 名.\n\nI need to push this to 名. Since I'm in a cron-triggered session, I should deliver the message. Let me announce it to the user.\n\nActually, since I'm in a cron-triggered isolated session, my plain text reply will be delivered to... hmm, the cron job had delivery settings. Let me check if I can push the message to 名.\n\nLooking at the cron more carefully - the delivery settings were probably configured in the cron job. The message says \"汀桑让我给你带句话\" which means I'm the one forwarding it. Let me just announce this message to 名.\n\nSince my reply is delivered as the final output, I should format it as the forwarded message for 名. But actually, the cron delivery's \"to\" field determines who receives this. Since it's a message intended for 名, I should deliver it to 名's QQ.\n\nLet me check how the cron was set up. The cron name is \"递话 名 最终\" - so this is the final delivery attempt. Let me mark it as delivered and push the message.\n\nAc